Package: coexpr
Title: Cross-species co-expression network analysis in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Martin", "Paliocha", , "martin.paliocha@nmbu.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implementation of cross-species comparative transcriptomics using
    co-expression networks based on GrÃ¸nvold & Hvidsten. Calculates co-expression
    correlation scores (CCS) and ortholog rank scores (ORS) to identify conserved
    gene regulation patterns across species without requiring directly comparable samples.
